---
This paper presents a method for the precise cable-guided landing of tethered drones based on a continuous velocity vector field that relies on the tether variables only. A video of the experiments can be seen in this [link](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nCo1yEIxcQY).

[Download paper here](https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/10141667)

Recommended citation: <b>R. R. Lima</b>, B. Martinez Rocamora and G. A. S. Pereira, &quot; Continuous Vector Fields for Precise Cable-Guided Landing of Tethered UAVs,&quot; in <i>IEEE Robotics and Automation Letters</i>, vol. 8, no. 7, pp. 4370-4377, July 2023, doi: 10.1109/LRA.2023.3281940.
